                    "description": "加密功能的核心是“明文分组→向量映射→矩阵乘法→模26→字符映射”，步骤如下：\n1. 明文预处理：\n   - 过滤非字母字符，统一转为大写；\n   - 按分组长度（2个字母一组）拆分，若长度为奇数，末尾填充X（映射为23）；\n2. 向量映射：将每组明文转换为2×1的数字向量；\n3. 矩阵乘法：用密钥矩阵与明文字向量做乘法，结果取模26；\n4. 字符映射：将密文向量转换回字母，拼接得到最终密文；\n5. 合法性检查：验证密钥矩阵是否为2×2，且行列式与26互素（确保可逆）。\n预期输出：输入明文“HELLO”（预处理后为“HELLO”，长度5，填充为“HELLOX”）、密钥矩阵[[3,3],[2,5]]，加密后密文为“TCSWXC”。",
                    "code": "class HillCipher:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.alphabet_size = 26  # 仅支持大写英文字母\n    \n    def _preprocess_plaintext(self, plaintext: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"预处理明文：过滤非字母、大写、填充X\"\"\"\n        processed = ''.join([c.upper() for c in plaintext if c.isalpha()])\n        # 填充X使长度为2的倍数\n        if len(processed) % 2 != 0:\n            processed += 'X'\n        return processed\n    \n    def _letter_to_num(self, letter: str) -> int:\n        return ord(letter) - ord('A')\n    \n    def _num_to_letter(self, num: int) -> str:\n        return chr(num + ord('A'))\n    \n    def _determinant_2x2(self, matrix: list) -> int:\n        \"\"\"计算2x2矩阵行列式\"\"\"\n        return matrix[0][0] * matrix[1][1] - matrix[0][1] * matrix[1][0]\n    \n    def _gcd(self, a: int, b: int) -> int:\n        while b:\n            a, b = b, a % b\n        return a\n    \n    def encrypt(self, plaintext: str, key_matrix: list) -> str:\n        \"\"\"2×2矩阵加密\"\"\"\n        # 检查密钥矩阵维度\n        if len(key_matrix) != 2 or len(key_matrix[0]) != 2:\n            raise ValueError(\"仅支持2×2密钥矩阵\")\n        \n        # 检查密钥矩阵可逆性\n        det = self._determinant_2x2(key_matrix) % self.alphabet_size\n        if self._gcd(det, self.alphabet_size) != 1:\n            raise ValueError(\"密钥矩阵不可逆，无法加密\")\n        \n        # 预处理明文\n        processed_plain = self._preprocess_plaintext(plaintext)\n        print(f\"预处理后明文：{processed_plain}\")\n        \n        ciphertext = \"\"\n        # 按2个字母一组处理\n        for i in range(0, len(processed_plain), 2):\n            # 转换为明文字向量\n            p0 = self._letter_to_num(processed_plain[i])\n            p1 = self._letter_to_num(processed_plain[i+1])\n            plain_vector = [p0, p1]\n            print(f\"第{i//2+1}组明文：{processed_plain[i:i+2]}→向量{plain_vector}\")\n            \n            # 矩阵乘法（2x2 × 2x1）\n            c0 = (key_matrix[0][0] * p0 + key_matrix[0][1] * p1) % self.alphabet_size\n            c1 = (key_matrix[1][0] * p0 + key_matrix[1][1] * p1) % self.alphabet_size\n            cipher_vector = [c0, c1]\n            print(f\"加密后向量：{cipher_vector}→字符{self._num_to_letter(c0)}{self._num_to_letter(c1)}\")\n            \n            # 拼接密文\n            ciphertext += self._num_to_letter(c0) + self._num_to_letter(c1)\n        \n        return ciphertext\n\n# 测试加密\ncipher = HillCipher()\nplaintext = \"HELLO\"\nkey_matrix = [[3, 3], [2, 5]]\nencrypted = cipher.encrypt(plaintext, key_matrix)\nprint(f\"最终密文：{encrypted}\")  # 预期输出：TCSWXC"
